三、課程大綱 Syllabus (本課程大綱教師得依實際教學進度及學生學習情況進行調整)


■  課程目標 (Course Objectives)In Composition II, you will learn:to organize essays in a logical order (time order, spatial order, emphatic order) and with proper 
transitions
to write a narrative essay that is developed inductively or deductively
to write well-organized descriptive paragraphs about a person or a place
to write a well-organized expository essay that has a clear thesis and supporting details
to write a well-organized summary-response essay on a selected article (to summarize, paraphrase, and quote)


■  課程內涵 (Course Contents)


■  多元教學方式 (Muliti-Teaching Methods)說明：除了課堂講授與考試測驗之外，本課程在學期中可能會運用到以下哪些教學方式，以期能進一步提升學生學習成效
    1.小組討論
2.實作示範或演示
3.期末報告/策展/發表
4.配合使用數位教學平臺(Moodle)或其他多媒體教學



■  主要參考書籍/資料 (Textbooks and References)
    (教科書遵守智慧財產權觀念不得非法影印)Wyrick, J. (2011). Steps to Writing Well with Additional Readings. (11th ed.). Boston: Thomson Wadsworth.    


■  本課程是否有使用原文書 是


